      caption: "\u{1F537} THREE INCOME STREAMS\n\u2726 Plan Yield + Referral Network + Leadership Bonus = Maximum Earnings\n\nTurboLoop doesn't limit you to a single source of income \u2014 it gives you three powerful engines working simultaneously. Engine 1: Plan Yield delivers 3% to 54% returns depending on your chosen plan, calculated and distributed daily by the smart contract. Engine 2: The 20-Level Referral Network distributes 51% of referred deposits across your entire downline \u2014 share your link and earn from every member who joins through your network, up to 20 levels deep. Engine 3: Leadership Bonuses reward community builders with an additional 1% to 10% based on your rank \u2014 from Partner to the legendary TURBO LEGEND tier. Each engine operates independently, meaning your total earnings are the sum of all three. Build all three, and you unlock TurboLoop's full earning potential.\n\n\u2705 Key Highlights:\n\u2022 Engine 1: Plan Yield \u2014 3% to 54% depending on plan, daily automatic\n\u2022 Engine 2: Referral Network \u2014 20 levels deep, 51% total distribution\n\u2022 Engine 3: Leadership Bonus \u2014 7 ranks, 1% to 10% additional earnings\n\u2022 All three engines operate simultaneously and independently\n\u2022 Total earnings = Plan Yield + Referral Commissions + Leadership Bonus\n\n\u{1F48E} Three engines. One goal: your wealth. Activate all three.\n\n\u{1F310} turboloop.io",
