      caption: "\u{1F537} 20-LEVEL REFERRAL NETWORK\n\u2726 One Link, 20 Levels Deep, 51% Distribution \u2014 Build Your Empire\n\nTurboLoop's referral network is one of the most generous in all of DeFi. When you share your unique referral link and someone joins, you earn a percentage of their deposits \u2014 not just from your direct referrals, but from 20 levels deep into your network. The total distribution across all 20 levels is 51%, making it one of the highest referral payouts in the industry. Level 1 (direct referrals) earns you 12%. Level 2 earns 8%. Level 3: 5%. Levels 4-5: 3% each. Levels 6-10: 2% each. Levels 11-20: 1% each. There's no limit on width \u2014 you can refer as many people as you want at each level. Payments are automatic and daily, processed by the smart contract without any manual claiming.\n\n\u2705 Key Highlights:\n\u2022 Level 1: 12% (direct referrals) \u2014 the highest single-level payout\n\u2022 Levels 2-5: 8%, 5%, 3%, 3% \u2014 totaling 31% across first 5 levels\n\u2022 Levels 6-10: 2% each \u2014 10% total from mid-depth network\n\u2022 Levels 11-20: 1% each \u2014 10% total from deep network\n\u2022 Grand total: 51% distribution across 20 levels, unlimited width\n\n\u{1F48E} One link. Twenty levels. Unlimited earnings potential.\n\n\u{1F310} turboloop.io",
