      caption: "\u{1F537} LEADERSHIP RANKS\n\u2726 Seven Tiers of Achievement \u2014 From Partner to TURBO LEGEND\n\nTurboLoop rewards its most dedicated community builders with seven prestigious leadership ranks, each unlocking progressively higher bonus percentages on your entire network's activity. Starting as a Partner with 100 team members earns you a 1% leadership bonus. As your network grows, you ascend through Senior Partner (2%), Manager (3%), Senior Manager (5%), Director (7%), and Senior Director (8%). At the pinnacle stands the TURBO LEGEND rank \u2014 reserved for those who build a team of 10,000+ members with $1M+ in total team deposits, earning a commanding 10% leadership bonus. These bonuses are in addition to your plan yields and referral commissions, creating a third powerful income stream for those who build.\n\n\u2705 Key Highlights:\n\u2022 Partner: 100 members \u2192 1% leadership bonus\n\u2022 Senior Partner: 250 members \u2192 2% bonus\n\u2022 Manager: 500 members \u2192 3% | Senior Manager: 1,000 members \u2192 5%\n\u2022 Director: 2,500 members \u2192 7% | Senior Director: 5,000 members \u2192 8%\n\u2022 TURBO LEGEND: 10,000 members + $1M team deposit \u2192 10% bonus\n\n\u{1F48E} Rise in rank. Earn more. The summit awaits the bold.\n\n\u{1F310} turboloop.io",
