      caption: "\u{1F537} ONBOARDING BONUS PROGRAM\n\u2726 Up to $10,000 in Rewards \u2014 For Those Who Build Fast\n\nTurboLoop's Onboarding Bonus is a time-limited acceleration program that rewards rapid community builders with substantial cash bonuses. Within a 60-day window, hit specific milestones and unlock escalating rewards: bring in 50 new members and earn $50. Reach 100 members for $200. Hit 250 for $750. Cross 500 for $2,000. Achieve 750 for $4,000. And the ultimate milestone \u2014 1,000 new members within 60 days \u2014 unlocks a massive $10,000 bonus. These bonuses are paid on top of your regular referral commissions and leadership bonuses, making the first 60 days the most lucrative period for network builders. The clock starts when you make your first referral.\n\n\u2705 Key Highlights:\n\u2022 50 members in 60 days \u2192 $50 bonus\n\u2022 100 members \u2192 $200 | 250 members \u2192 $750\n\u2022 500 members \u2192 $2,000 | 750 members \u2192 $4,000\n\u2022 1,000 members \u2192 $10,000 \u2014 the ultimate milestone\n\u2022 Bonuses are additional to referral commissions and leadership rewards\n\n\u{1F48E} Invite. Earn. Repeat. The first 60 days are golden.\n\n\u{1F310} turboloop.io",
